These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, skydiving, sudoku, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, drama, adventure, zombie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, golf, badminton, soccer
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, quad-bike, van, trike
 1. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##8
 2. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
 3. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is not to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##8
 5. the person driving the tram is not to the right of the person driving the tram##8
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 8. the person watching zombie movies is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's sport is golf##2
 9. the person driving the trike is the person watching adventure movies##1
10. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
13. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
14. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person driving the van##1
15. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not the person who's sport is golf##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles     | skydiving   | writing | sudoku |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | zombie   | martial-arts   | adventure  |
| Sport         | golf  | badminton  | soccer  | baseball |
| Transport     | tram    | van | quad-bike     | trike    |

