.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, tea, fanta
There 4 different types of food: apricot, artichoke, cauliflower, garlic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, techno, electronic, dubstep
4 different pets are kept: snake, lizard, turtle, hamster
 1. the fan of electronic is between the owner of the snake and the fan of techno##2
 2. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the owner of the lizard##8
 3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
 4. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8
 5. the owner of the snake is not to the left of the fan of techno##8
 6. the person eating garlic is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
 7. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 8. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of country is the owner of the lizard##1
10. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
11. the owner of the snake is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
12. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
13. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the person eating artichoke##5
14. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
15. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
17. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the fan of techno##8
18. the person eating artichoke is not to the right of the owner of the lizard##8
19. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | coffee | tea | fanta  | 7up  |
| Food          | garlic     | artichoke | apricot | cauliflower  |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | electronic  | dubstep | country |
| Pet           | turtle | hamster | snake    | lizard  |

