 2. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person watching documentary movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
 7. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
11. the person watching documentary movies is not to the left of the fan of ambient##8
12. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3

.:: Answer ::.
