 4. the person eating strawberry is between the coach and the nurse##2
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the person eating strawberry##8
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the librarian##1
10. the nurse is the person who's sport is badminton##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person eating broccoli##8
12. the coach is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
13. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
14. the nurse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
15. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
