 8. the mechanic is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the person drinking cola##7
 9. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
10. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
11. the software-developer is on the right of the fisherman##1
12. the mechanic is not the colombian##6
13. the australian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
14. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
