There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, almond-milk, juice
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, pop, punk, r&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball, rowing, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, van, airplane, scooter
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 2. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
 6. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 8. the person driving the van is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
10. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the fan of pop##8
11. the fan of punk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
12. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | juice     | almond-milk    | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | r&b      | punk     | pop     |
| Sport         | skiing | rowing  | sailing     | volleyball  |
| Transport     | jet-ski     | airplane | scooter | van     |

