.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, mirinda, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, dancing, singing, photography
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, salsa, electronic, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: french, pakistani, mexican, turkish
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the turkish##1
 2. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
 3. the person drinking tea is the fan of salsa##1
 4. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the fan of punk##5
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the left of the fan of gospel##8
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 8. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 9. the pakistani is not to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##8
10. the fan of electronic is not the french##6
11. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
12. the turkish is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
13. the fan of punk is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
14. the french is on the right of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | water      | tea  | mirinda | iced-tea        |
| Hobby         | photography | dancing   | video-games   | singing |
| Music-Genre   | punk    | salsa   | electronic    | gospel      |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | turkish | mexican   | french    |

