.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, soy-milk, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, photographer, dressmaker, writer
4 different pets are kept: mouse, guinea-pig, dog, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, jet-ski, car, trike
 1. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 2. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the photographer##8
 3. the owner of the mouse is the person drinking 7up##1
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
 6. the person driving the trike is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the writer is not to the right of the person driving the trike##8
 8. the dressmaker is on the far right##1
 9. the photographer is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
10. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
12. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
13. the person driving the car is not to the left of the writer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | almond-milk          | 7up | soy-milk        | cola    |
| Job         | writer | teacher   | photographer | dressmaker  |
| Pet         | dog           | mouse     | horse       | guinea-pig  |
| Transport   | trike            | car   | jet-ski     | train |

