.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, almond-milk, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, drawing, magic-tricks, sudoku
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, firefighter, police-officer, paramedic
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, tram, skateboard, snowmobile
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
 2. the videographer is not to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##8
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person driving the tram##1
 4. the videographer is not to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
 5. the firefighter is somewhere to the right of the police-officer##5
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
 8. the person drinking juice is not to the left of the police-officer##8
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
10. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person driving the snowmobile and the paramedic##7
11. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea        | juice        | mirinda   |
| Hobby       | drawing      | fishing      | sudoku | magic-tricks |
| Job         | paramedic | police-officer | firefighter     | videographer  |
| Transport   | skateboard          | boat      | tram     | snowmobile  |

