.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, writing, skydiving, hiking
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, freelancer, manager, firefighter
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, action, spy, family
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, soul, disco, rock
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the left of the lawyer##8
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the fan of rock is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5
 4. the firefighter is the person watching family movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not the manager##6
 6. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the fan of soul##8
 7. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the manager##8
 8. the manager is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
 9. the fan of disco is in an even position##4
10. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
11. the person watching disaster movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the manager and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
13. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | hiking    | skydiving   | fishing   | writing |
| Job           | lawyer | freelancer    | manager | firefighter    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy   | disaster | action     | family    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | disco      | soul         | rock     |

 